'''Asad Afridi''' ({{lang-ur|{{Nastaliq|اسد آفریدی}}}}), was a [[Pakistan]]i [[cricket]]er who played for [[Sukkur cricket team|Sukkur]].

Asad made a single first-class appearance for the team, during the 1976-77 season, against [[Hyderabad cricket team (Pakistan)|Hyderabad]]. He scored 9 runs from the lower-middle order in the only innings in which he batted.

